<paragraph id="8BF9369BFFFDED365201D3DBA3545220" blockId="39.[264,1324,1693,1839]" pageId="39" pageNumber="40">
Coloration as described by 
<bibRefCitation id="EFD74B6AFFFDED365142D3DBA5F253B8" author="Distant" box="[587,761,1693,1719]" pageId="39" pageNumber="48" refString="Distant, W. L. (1918) Rhynchota Volume VII, Homoptera and Appendix. Heteroptera: Addenda. In: Shipley, A. E. &amp; Marshall, G. A. K. (Eds) The Fauna of British India including Ceylon and Burma. Taylor and Francis, London, pp. 1 - 210." type="book chapter" year="1918">
