<number id="3D8E24BCFFFDED3651B9D3DBA5FB53B8" box="[688,752,1693,1719]" pageId="39" pageNumber="40" value="1918.0">1918</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
. The median two spindle­shaped elongate spots on vertex broader, remaining four on either side of these of similar width, sometimes reaching hind margin of vertex. Upper part of face with an arched dark brown line. Scutellum with median brown stripes in addition to dark brown basal triangles.
</paragraph>
